high_descs: Turn to the garbage can, on the floor to your right.
Pull out the bar of soap inside the garbage can.
Move to your right, away from the sink, then go across the room to the last sink on your left.
Place the bar of soap in the sink, turn the water on, rinse the soap off, turn the water off, and remove the bar of soap from the sink.
Place the bar of soap in the right cabinet, under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap under the sink.

put the pink bar in the sink, wash the bar, take it out
turn around, turn around to the cabinet under the sink
open the right door, put the pink bar in

high_descs: turn right and head for the bin
pick up the soap from the bin
